                     <interp inst="t18760403-324-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>, Stealing a silver tankard and other articles of <persName id="t18760403-name-352" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18760403-name-352" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18760403-name-352" type="surname" value="FIELDING"></interp>
